  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<blockquote>文化传统，庙堂是本姓宗族活动的地方，不方便安排他人。不要说他人，哪怕是儿媳妇，留个痕迹都不容易。网传黄山西递有个汪家祠堂留有欧姓的牌子，因欧是汪家媳妇主政多年支撑了汪家，破例才给了她一个牌子。要多么忠心才会把老祖宗赶走，腾出位子来给别人坐。让别人坐，别人，正常人，也不会坐，那不吉利。下面那个万兽无僵，不是没几年就僵了么。</blockquote><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTYzMjEwYjI4ZWFmYmUyODE0YzgxLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNDQwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a63210b28eafbe2814c81.jpg?width=1440&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a63210b28eafbe2814c81.jpg?width=1440&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a63210b28eafbe2814c81.jpg?width=1440&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTgzM2FjYmU3M2JkN2ZlNDJmYjU5LmpwZz93aWR0aD05MzMmaGVpZ2h0PTY5OQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e833acbe73bd7fe42fb59.jpg?width=933&amp;height=699\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e833acbe73bd7fe42fb59.jpg?width=933&amp;height=699\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e833acbe73bd7fe42fb59.jpg?width=933&amp;height=699\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
